{"tid":1165611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國擬將海康威視（中國最大CCTV生產商）列入黑名單","createTime":"2019-05-22T01:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T06:23:13.000Z","uid":13663,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"576d931d3223a2cae0a4cd66041877dfdf077bce","tid":1165611,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T01:54:12.000Z","msg":"美國擬將海康威視列入黑名單<br />\n財訊快報 &middot; 801人追蹤<br />\n劉敏夫1 小時前<br />\n【財訊快報／劉敏夫】外電引述《紐約時報》的報導指出，美國方面考慮將中國安全防護視頻監控產品生產商海康威視(002415 CH)列入黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》引述知情人士消息指出，川普政府正在考慮限制海康威視。美國政府官員可能會在未來幾週做出最終決定。<br />\n<br />\n針對海康威視的措施或與對華為的要求類似。美國商務部可將其列入實體名單，要求美國公司在與海康威視進行業務往來之前須獲得批准。<br />\n<br />\n對於上述消息，美國商務部和白宮不予評論；海康威視未回應置評請求。"},{"pid":"9824eb003a3cb1e53e0d047d175c70f4e84ac581","tid":1165611,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T01:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dda3d018fecda6eec77385eca3acb33f2b5c36d","tid":1165611,"uid":13663,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T01:56:49.000Z","msg":"冇左海康 中國監控系統隨時崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ea4838c29c1af3e1bfc81b76a674da90f00f94","tid":1165611,"uid":51720,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T01:57:11.000Z","msg":"冇得賣各類記憶體、SSD 等產品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c972125e1fdb1f37e18ae40e437f19ee052de5","tid":1165611,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T01:57:27.000Z","msg":"開始越玩越縮水"},{"pid":"621c7dcc5d9ca688ad31f0bbe11d66473ef2b218","tid":1165611,"uid":21917,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T01:57:36.000Z","msg":"日日都有新野入list <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973b34f819a4c1cdf958d10c72f2758d3ad5ba73","tid":1165611,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T01:57:38